{"tid":1632893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［攬攬］唔好話勇武做太多 和理試著說我都想幫手","createTime":"2019-10-07T00:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T01:00:29.000Z","uid":262709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cb490b2f44a1b3f95ec782bb28331842c6fc6cf5","tid":1632893,"uid":262709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:51:56.000Z","msg":"辛苦勇武仔， <br />\n喂你咁攰 咁勁 得唔得架😍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBeneath the mask is more than flesh <br />\nBut afterall we are flesh!<br />\n我地都係人 我地都有自己的限制<br />\n和理有 勇武有<br />\n<br />\n不分和勇 我地每個人都都做多啲！！！<br />\n<br />\n喂<br />\n和理們 <br />\n我地係時候真係做多啲<br />\n除左被動罷乜罷乜<br />\n人地深入敵陣 我地都可以 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n街站？<br />\n茶餐廳遊說工作？<br />\n連儂連儂 痴爆佢？<br />\n商場唱歌<br />\n我都係想拋磚引舊玉地番來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地班警咁on9 都識攬實手足唔放<br />\n我地咁醒 咁善良 成班手足要攬實呀<br />\n我地幫手解話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地真係輸唔起 輸唔起！！<br />\n唔該 嘈之前諗下新屋嶺 諗下被人拉既手足😭"},{"pid":"fa4d8b05a35376981c2ee20ee8d7d26ee1ef07ee","tid":1632893,"uid":262709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:58:59.000Z","msg":"自推！！"},{"pid":"2f920be1a1c45b4634d0ecdc8acbbd8270b31440","tid":1632893,"uid":262709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:00:16.000Z","msg":"動之以情呀！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人其實好易哄！！！<br />\n我地要贏！"},{"pid":"3a4c79fe7354cc4184907a5302060860e98b6066","tid":1632893,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:00:29.000Z","msg":"明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.g